OL,3,CAndy Burnham says first day of work at
OL,4,CNo. 10 North is 'best day of my life'
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has described his first
OL,7,Fday of work at the new No 10 North in
OL,8,FManchester as the "best day of my
OL,9,Flife".
OL,11,FSpeaking as he opened the new centre
OL,12,Fof Government base in Manchester, the
OL,13,FPrime Minister said: "I cannot tell
OL,14,Fyou what a proud moment this is.
OL,16,F"I think this might be the best day of
OL,17,Fmy life. I'm not joking either. I know
OL,18,Fyou think I am, but I'm not.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@EO]uD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
