CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784917111
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says first day of work at
OL,4,CNo. 10 North is 'best day of my life'
OL,6,F"Things are just completely coming
OL,7,Ffull circle here for me, and to be
OL,8,Fhere with you all in the heart of
OL,9,FManchester this Friday morning, at the
OL,10,Fend of a fairly big week, is just
OL,11,Feverything to me because it's almost
OL,12,Fexactly 35 years since I left this
OL,13,Fcity as a recently graduated young man
OL,14,Fwho couldn't find a job in the city.
OL,16,F"It (Manchester) was in a pretty bad
OL,17,Fplace at that time, it's fair to say,
OL,18,Fthis is the because the 80s had turned
OL,19,Finto the 90s, there wasn't much.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784917111
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says first day of work at
OL,4,CNo. 10 North is 'best day of my life'
OL,6,F"That really is an experience that
OL,7,FI've never forgotten, my generation of
OL,8,Fpeople growing up here. And it's true
OL,9,Fof places all over the country to get
OL,10,Fon in life, you had to leave where you
OL,11,Fwhere you were because things weren't
OL,12,Fhere.
OL,14,F"The country has always been a little
OL,15,Flike that, hasn't it? That opportunity
OL,16,Fhas not been evenly spread around the
OL,17,Fcountry, and not all places have felt
OL,18,Fthat they are part of the national
OL,19,Fstory, and that is what this
OL,20,FGovernment is going to work every
OL,21,Fsingle day to change.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784917111
OL,3,CAndy Burnham says first day of work at
OL,4,CNo. 10 North is 'best day of my life'
OL,6,F"And that is what No 10 North is all
OL,7,Fabout: putting power in every postcode
OL,8,Fso that people can turn things around
OL,9,Ffor themselves and make changes, just
OL,10,Fas this great city has done, and the
OL,11,Fother English cities are doing through
OL,12,Fdevolution, turning things round
OL,13,Fbecause of that ability to be able to
OL,14,Fdo more for themselves.
OL,16,FAnd it's also about getting the whole
OL,17,Fcountry facing the same way, and then
OL,18,Fpulling in the same direction, that I
OL,19,Fthink is what No 10 North can achieve."
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@gO]
